Commentary Text: Suyash Sharma to Gaikwad, out Bowled!! Off stump out of the ground! Gaikwad has been totally deceived by young Suyash Sharma! Commentary Text: Tushar Deshpande to N Jagadeesan, out Caught by Jadeja!! Both the openers gone! 134.8kph, full delivery that swings away marginally outside off, Jagadeesan moves slightly leg-side and throws his arms at it. The ball flies off the outer edge and threatens to dip. However Jadeja takes a superb running catch. Came in and also to his left from third man before bending low to snaffle it. Made it look so easy. N Jagadeesan c Jadeja b Tushar Deshpande 1(3)
